scopecontent.p:
This is a collection of the papers of Hans Ris. Materials include: photographs
                    (transmission electron micrographs and high voltage electron microscope images);
                    drafts and galley proofs of articles; correspondence with colleagues; class
                    notes and lab notebooks; notes from conferences and poster sessions; articles by
                    others; correspondence with and records related to postdoctoral fellows;
                    correspondence related to his visits to Russia and China; and illustrations.
